    <item>
      <title>普京上任前夕下令进行战术核演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在他第五任期就职前一天，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令俄罗斯军队进行涉及战术核武器的作战演习，加剧了他与西方的对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 07:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与菲律宾在台湾附近的小岛上举行演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-holds-drills-with-the-philippines-at-tiny-island-near-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一中午之前，黑鹰直升机降落在伊巴亚特，带领美国和菲律宾海军陆战队的一个排在这个东南亚国家最北端有人居住的岛屿上进行罕见的军事演习。也是距离台湾最近的地区之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-holds-drills-with-the-philippines-at-tiny-island-near-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:21:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
